<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Control_theory&action=edit&section=21.php.html" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><span class="citation book">Levine, William S., ed. (1996). <i>The Control Handbook</i>. New York: CRC Press. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/978-0-8493-8570-4" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-8493-8570-4">978-0-8493-8570-4</a>.</span></li>
