<li><span class="citation book">Franklin et al. (2002). <i>Feedback Control of Dynamic Systems</i> (4 ed.). New Jersey: Prentice Hall. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/0-13-032393-4" title="Special:BookSources/0-13-032393-4">0-13-032393-4</a>.</span></li>
